            <title>[FELIX-5955] Move changelog.txt to toplevel project dir</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-5955</link>
                <project id="12310100" key="FELIX">Felix</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently, chanlogs are stored in each dependency manager sub projects.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;But the download felix link requires the changelog to be located at the toplevel source project directory. Moreover, it&apos;s easier to maintain one single changelog.txt file instead of having one for each DM sub projects.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;let&apos;s have a single changelog.txt file stored in the DM toplevel source directory (dependencymanager/changelog;txt).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

